    public class SymphonicaAdapter
extends hn.com.tigo.josm.common.adapter.AbstractAdapter<hn.com.tigo.josm.orchestrator.driver.symphonica.SymphonicaDriver>
    The Class SymphonicaAdapter class singleton, used to manage the configuration for attributes Throughput and TimeOut for tasks in SymphonicaAdapter .This attributes come from ConfigurationJosm service from SymphonicaAdapter.xml. Also create a Driver's Pool to manage the maintenance threads execution and monitoring.
